{"tid":1873711,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[警世post]唔好亂咁封喉","createTime":"2020-02-10T19:42:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T07:31:31.000Z","uid":84116,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"09d37bad1579d0fe77e62f9ed90da3c82e114ddf","tid":1873711,"uid":84116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T19:42:32.000Z","msg":"封咗有機會爆喉或者屎水倒灌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有異味發出應該即刻搵師傅上去睇。無論個設計幾舊都好，都唔會有異味湧入間屋，有異味姐係代表有地方漏氣，可能係有d配件要更換。"},{"pid":"beeb5e2a606968a104bf98ca674d7e5b7e1c1f2e","tid":1873711,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T19:46:18.000Z","msg":"屌聽日即搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f36b9aa7ed7dadabccce853e3b083fa9f9b2cd6","tid":1873711,"uid":202011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T19:49:10.000Z","msg":"多謝提醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"661c72de7c3e75638881a8fe5c177931ab4e30a2","tid":1873711,"uid":84116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T20:03:05.000Z","msg":"仲有u trap上面個粒的有佢嘅用途，下面個網有講<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c02tVBc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc02tVBc.jpg&h=0e980039&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vSpTngd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvSpTngd.png&h=c16e4637&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dux.co.nz/product-category/wastewater-traps/vented-traps/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dux.co.nz%2Fproduct-category%2Fwastewater-traps%2Fvented-traps%2F&d=u5wkwi0qRaq%2FdbVqa5yG4ZMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=0494897d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dux.co.nz/product-category/wastewater-traps/vented-traps/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Vented trap with air admission valve (AAV) eases syphonic action, reduces noise and protects the water seal</span>"},{"pid":"124cb583377419de1a424f56d5b29bcfd1abaca6","tid":1873711,"uid":84116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T06:55:40.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n凸出黎個舊野叫air admittance valve，至於俗稱小弟真係唔知叫咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nHow an Air Admittance Valve (AAV) Works<br />\n<br />\nAn air admittance valve&nbsp;(AAV), sometimes called an&nbsp;auto vent, is a device attached to the fixture drain line. It has a mechanism that <span style=\"color: red;\">opens up to admit room air into the drain</span> under the force of the negative pressure <span style=\"color: red;\">caused by water flowing</span> through the drain. With this negative pressure dissipated, the water in the drain trap cannot be siphoned off. Once the <span style=\"color: red;\">water stops flowing</span> and the negative pressure ends, the AAV <span style=\"color: red;\">device automatically closes to prevent sewer gases from entering the room</span>.<br />\n<br />\n簡單d黎講姐係舊野會自動開關，如果有異味係呢個位滲出姐係舊野壞咗要換而唔係封咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thespruce.com/sink-vent-installing-an-auto-vent-2718828\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thespruce.com%2Fsink-vent-installing-an-auto-vent-2718828&d=u5wkwi0qRaq%2FdbVqa5yG4ZMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=4dc259ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thespruce.com/sink-vent-installing-an-auto-vent-2718828</a>"},{"pid":"5cc1a6f23416e3ad1c76143e6b51803de3a95828","tid":1873711,"uid":84116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T07:31:31.000Z","msg":"下面條片有講個valve點運作<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MUha2Xp9HGs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMUha2Xp9HGs&d=u5wkwi0qRaq%2FdbVqa5yG4ZMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=1aec0047\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MUha2Xp9HGs</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cy16L4M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCy16L4M.jpg&h=5f974a66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ayVjmC7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FayVjmC7.jpg&h=543e77dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4：50開始<br />\n<br />\n呢條片講冇空氣入去水喉會點，就係會抽走u trap入面嘅水<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zGofkKOP2SU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzGofkKOP2SU&d=u5wkwi0qRaq%2FdbVqa5yG4ZMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=284c77f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zGofkKOP2SU</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">簡單d黎講姐係只有屋嘅空氣入條渠，而渠嘅臭氣唔可以入屋</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}